HasHumanReadableLabel
public class NPlusOneAryPredicate<X>
extends NPlusOneAryFunction<X,​java.lang.Boolean>
A descriptor for a predicate f( {x1, x2, ..., xN}, xx) where the x_i and xx are of the same type, and f is a boolean.

This is semantically almost the same as a predicate that takes N+1 values of type X, except that there are cases where it is more convenient to break them up into a group of N plus a single value of 1.
